<p><strong>Show notes for Mac Geek Gab Podcast For September 29th, 2008</strong></p>
<p>Dave and John share their findings on the expected longevity of recordable CDs and DVDs, then answer your questions relating to all things Mac.  Lots of good stuff here, folks.  Subscribe for free today!</p>
